<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Aw, Nang na umna cheng ka tha'n nuom a sai,
 Gimtheih ka thawkin ka hun sam;
 Nicheng ka kinepna, zankhuo-a ka la,
 Ka lungtup, ka damna ka bangkim.

[V2]
 2. Ei vengpa ngaihum, khawitaka um Na him?
 Belamte hehpih a puiin?
 Bangding in thihna luiguom ah ka kap dem?
 Zie khawvel gamthip a vakvai in?

[V3]
 3. Bangding in Na kawm apat ka taimang dem?
 Gamgaw-a gilkiela kapin?
 Na melma'n ka dahmel mu leh lawpin tin,
 Ka mittui mu leh nuihmel pu'na.

[V4]
 4. Hukdampa ngaih, Na mel ei muhsak zingin,
 Na lungmuonna chuh ei pien la;
 Na hehpih ngaihdamna kihetna nuom chun,
 Ka tha lungkham, thawmhau muon sakin.

[V5]
 5. Angel zatam na mel mu'n a kipak ui,
 Na tawngkam suok a ngak zing ui;
 Na kamsuok kumsawta mang loin a gii,
 Kumkhuo'n Lalpa A hun chawian ui.</lyrics>
<title>O THOU IN WHOSE PRESENCE</title>
<hymn_number>184</hymn_number>
</song>